2007;;Americanizing Shelley;;American;;Lorraine Senna;;Beau Bridges, Namrata Singh Gujral;;romantic comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Americanizing_Shelley;;In the film, Gujral stars as Shalini Singh/Shelley, an Indian woman who comes to the United States from a Himalayan village to find her fiance and crosses paths with a movie producer who tries to "Americanize" her in order to make her a star.